  "Launchpad/token signals — GoPlus honeypot flag": "Launchpad/token sinyalleri — GoPlus honeypot bayrağı",
  "List active signals. Filter with <code>?asset=</code>, <code>?signal_type=</code>, <code>?urgency=</code>, <code>?direction=</code>, and <code>?asset_class=</code> (<code>crypto</code> · <code>stock</code> · <code>metal</code> · <code>commodity</code> · <code>index</code>) to scope to crypto or the tokenized stock market": "Aktif sinyalleri listeler. Kripto veya tokenize hisse senedi piyasasına daraltmak için <code>?asset=</code>, <code>?signal_type=</code>, <code>?urgency=</code>, <code>?direction=</code> ve <code>?asset_class=</code> (<code>crypto</code> · <code>stock</code> · <code>metal</code> · <code>commodity</code> · <code>index</code>) ile filtreleyin",
  "Listed-options open-interest walls + aggregate max pain (CBOE, delayed) for a stock/index — the equity-market analogue of liquidation clusters. Strike walls act as magnets/pins into expiry.": "Listelenmiş-opsiyon açık-pozisyon duvarları + toplam max pain (CBOE, gecikmeli) bir hisse/endeks için — likidasyon kümelerinin hisse-piyasası karşılığı. Strike duvarları vade sonuna doğru mıknatıs/çivi gibi davranır.",
